description:
Help Tiny Tinga the monkey find his way home in this exciting INTERACTIVE BEDTIME STORY. Tickle the dastardly creatures who are out to stop Tiny Tinga until they giggle and fall over.

Discover secret sounds and animations, enjoy narration by the author and the Tickle Bar: tickle the baddies until the tickle bar runs out and the baddies run off.

---------------
FEATURES
---------------
- BEAUTIFUL story and unique characters.
- PLAY with the characters.
- DISCOVER secret sounds and animations in the surroundings.
- ENJOY a fun rhyming narration or read the book yourself.
- AUTOPLAY for young children and anybody who just wants to sit back and enjoy the story.

From the makers of top rated books: The Smelly Sprout, Princess Chocolate, The Boy Giant and Little Red Riding Hood. Featured in NEW AND NOTEWORTHY and WHAT'S HOT!

So get your Tickle Finger ready and help Tiny Tinga find his way home. You'll be tickled pink!

-----------------------------
MORE TICKLING?
-----------------------------

Get Tickle Finger Under the Sea and Tickle Finger and the Dinosaurs.
